These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, photographer
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the photographer##3
2. the photographer is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | paramedic | photographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | jazz |

 #################################

 
